name: File_Description
value: Stream water chemistry data for Green Lake 1, 1985 - 2010.

name: Dataset_Title
value: Stream water chemistry data for Green Lake 1, 1985 - 2010.

name: Dataset_Location
value: Sampling location was at the plate weir where the stream emerges from the base of the Green Lake 1 dam, i.e. after drainage through the dam. Original data are stored with the NWT LTER data manager.

name: Dataset_Abstract
value: This is a summary of major ion concentrations for stream water samples collected at the outlet stream from Green Lake 1. Sampling point was at the plate weir where the stream emerges from the base of the lake dam, i.e. after drainage through the dam.

name: Dataset_Methods
value: Methods can be found in the metadata associated with this dataset at niwot.colorado.edu/data/data/stream-water-chemistry-data-for-green-lake-1-1985-2010
